BRAZIL-NORTH COAST.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY BY M/V HAWK EXPLORER
   TOWING 5.4 MILE LONG CABLES:
   A. IN PROGRESS UNTIL 05 APR
      ALONG TRACKLINE BETWEEN
      00-02S 040-13W AND 02-05S 040-13W.
   B. 06 AND 07 APR ALONG TRACKLINE BETWEEN
      00-31S 039-30W AND 02-19S 039-30W.
   C. 08 AND 09 APR ALONG TRACKLINE BETWEEN
      01-32S 039-19W AND 01-32S 041-18W.
   SEVEN MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 10 APR.
